        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ <rs key="#Copy">Exemplum</rs> ex autentico relevatum. + In nomine domini
                        Dei eterni. Anno ab incarnacione domini nostri Iesu Christi millesimo CXXXV,
                        indicione XII, quintodecimo die mensis februaiii. Quem ad meritum anime mee
                        pertinere potest, necesse est mihi semper illud agere unde in hoc et in
                        futuro seculo plenam apud Dominum possim consegui mercedem. Ideo ego
                            <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Salian #Testamentum #Slave #Landed_possessions #parentOf"
                            ref="#people/3571">Albertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio</rs>, qui professus sum ex nacione mea lege
                        vivere <rs key="#Salian">Salicha</rs>, volo et statuo omnes <rs key="#Slave"
                            >servos atque ancillas</rs> meas post hobitum meum esse <rs
                            key="#Freedman">liberos et absolutos ab omni vinculo servitutis</rs> et
                        cives <rs key="#Roman">Romanos</rs>, omni suo peculio eis concesso. <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Terram</rs> quam a me tenent volo ut ab <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2427">Sancti
                            Petri</orgName> de <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/4139"
                            >Villanova</placeName> pro <rs key="#Beneficium">beneficio</rs> teneant,
                        et serviant de suis negociis in <orgName key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/503"><rs key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches"
                                >episcopatu</rs>
                            <placeName
                                key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches #Monasteries #Cities #Bishops"
                                ref="#places/59">Veronensi</placeName></orgName>
                        <orgName key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2428">et
                                <placeName key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches" ref="#places/69"
                                >Vicentino</placeName></orgName>. Volo etiam <persName
                            key="#childOf">Bonefacium</persName> et <persName key="#childOf"
                            >Garsendonium</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filios</rs> meos habere quicquid mihi pertinet in
                            <geogName key="#Curtes #Mansi" ref="#estates/2989"><rs key="#Curtes"
                                >curte</rs> de <placeName key="#Curtes #Mansi" ref="#places/4140"
                                >Menervii</placeName></geogName>, exceptis duobus <rs key="#Mansi"
                            >mansis</rs> quos <persName key="#childOf #Mansi #Countess"
                            >Garsinde</persName> filie mee relinquo, et de Zerpa, necnon de
                        Montecleda, et in Sancta Iohanne Bretone, illud Sancti Iohannis eorum parte
                        pro feudo possidente. <orgName key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">Sanctus
                            autem Benedictus</orgName> habeat quicquid mihi pertinet <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario iure</rs> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4141">Tresenta</placeName>, in <placeName
                            ref="#places/2990">Mulo</placeName> et in omnibus locis a <placeName
                            key="Rivers"><rs key="Rivers">flumine</rs> Athesis</placeName> usque ad
                        Ilbitum et Vadum de Capris. <rs key="#Monasteries">Monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/90">Sancti
                            Çenonis</orgName> et <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2429"
                            key="#Monasteries">Sancte Trinitatis</orgName> et <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2430" key="#Monasteries">Sancti Firmi</orgName>
                        habeant quicquid mihi pertinet in <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs> Verone vel
                        extra Veronam, usque ad Flubium, excepta terra quam habeo iuxta murum
                        civitatis quam Enrico de Artvicho ad proprium relinquo, preterea <rs
                            key="#Castle">castrum</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle #Curtes" ref="#places/4138">Sancti
                            Bonefacii</placeName> cum tota <geogName ref="#estates/2990" key="#Curtes">curte</geogName>,
                        exceptis tribus mansis quos Garsinde iudico. Necnon castrum de <placeName
                            key="#Castle #Curtes" ref="#places/2477">Monteforte</placeName> cum tota
                        <geogName ref="#estates/2991" key="#Curtes">curte</geogName> episcopatui Verone relinquo, eo
                        silicet ordine ut <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count #Feudum #siblingOf">Albertus</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Count #Feudum #siblingOf">Rambaldus</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Count #Feudum #siblingOf">Bonefacius</persName> de
                            <placeName>Magreda</placeName> habeant pro <rs key="#Feudum">feudo</rs>
                        ex parte eiusdem episcopatus, et serviant infra
                            <placeName>Mincium</placeName> et <placeName>Plavum</placeName>. Et si
                        Rambaldus decesserit, <rs key="#siblingOf">fratres</rs> eius cum eis
                        comuniter habeant, et si aliquis eorum sine filiis decesserit, unus alteri
                        succedat. Similiter volo ut isti tres habeant Concam de Albaro ad proprium
                        et persolvant dotem <rs key="#Countess">comitisse</rs> Garsinde que ei iure
                        debetur. Marsilium vero et filios Agnetis volo ut habeant totum quod mihi
                        perlinet in <orgName key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/223">episcopatu <placeName
                                key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches #Cities" ref="#places/41"
                                >Pataviensi</placeName></orgName> extra civitatem, ita ut Marsilius
                        medietatem habeat. Quicquid autem proprietatis mee in civitate est, <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">hospitale</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2431" key="#Hospitals">Sancti
                            Sepulchri</orgName> de <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/914"
                            >Venecia</placeName> habeat. <orgName key="#Churches">Ecclesia de
                                <placeName ref="#places/259" key="#Churches"
                            >Runco</placeName></orgName> et <orgName key="#Churches">de <placeName
                                ref="#places/4144" key="#Churches">Zerpa</placeName></orgName>
                        habeant proprietatem <rs key="#Islands">insule</rs> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/4142" key="#Islands">Scardevara</placeName>, usufructum
                        autem Bonefacio propinquo meo si decessero usque dum vivit relinquo;
                        similiter volo ut omnes res quas mihi donavit in eum deveniant. Insuper
                        statuo terram quam habeo in <placeName ref="#places/4143"
                            >Montebello</placeName> et per totum Vicentinum episcopatum a Montebello
                        in territorio Sancti Felicis episcopatus habeat. Terra de Conca de Albaro
                        quam filii Bosketti a me tenent ecclesia Sancte Zacharie habeat, ita ut ipsi
                        pro feudo teneant ***. Signa manuum <persName key="#Bishops #Witness"><rs
                                key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> Veronensis</persName>, <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abas</rs> Calavene, <rs key="#Archpriests"
                            >archipresbiter</rs> Sancti Georgii, presbiter Richardus de Sancto
                        Benedicto <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. Signa manuum Ardericus de
                        Montesello, Enricus de Bonadico, Wiçardus de Noventa, Ambrosius, Nordillus
                        de Lunico testes. Signa manuum Benenatus, Ugo de Çerpa, Enricus de Artvicho
                            <rs>iurisperiti</rs>, Caverlattus, Ubertus de Çerpa, Paganus de Sancto
                        Bonefacio testes. Ego <persName key="#Notary #Testamentum #Writer"><name
                                ref="Albertus">Albertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> hanc <rs key="#Testamentum"
                            >ordinacionem</rs> rogatus <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et complevi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
